.description
Easy-to-use pay analysis program which is easily configured to deal with
the way deductions are made from your salary.  Useful for investigating
just how large a slice of your hard earned cash ends up in the hands of the
tax man, or to make sure that your employer isn't deducting more from your
wages than he should.  
